@host = http://localhost:5099

### Ingest OHLCV for BTC + ETH into the DB
POST {{host}}/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{ "assets": ["BTC", "ETH"], "days": 180 }

### List assets + candle count
GET {{host}}/assets

### Latest OHLCV data for BTC
GET {{host}}/candles?symbol=BTC&limit=10&order=desc

### Generate the PDF report
POST {{host}}/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{ "assets": ["BTC", "ETH"] }
